reviews.review_text: incomplete i havent downloaded this yet but i see its decievingly incomplete(Not Fade Away of is missing)... as i continue to look for a complete SBD of a 1980 warfield show

The best of (except incomplete at the end) the weekend acoustic sets ! I originally wrote this back when there were less available recordings and didn't listen to the end since as I say below hence my rating in deceasing. On the otherhand there is more here than several other shows, sadly. I can't comment on the week day ones since I wasn't there.
     The electric is O.K. but as I said elsehere in general, they are rather mediocre!
Besides the fact that is board tape is missing the end.
     Moreover, as others have reminded me even though modestly speaking given that below; I seem to have forgotten, even the following point wasn't as great as others given that is that I'm fairly certain I have seen every performance of John Chipollina (in the missing part) except one other (I think that was the Mosconi (spelling?) memorial or at that venue?); unless he showed up in the very early days, otherwise I would have remembered If you like him see: both Winterland 78-10-22(Sun) & Berkeley Greek 83-5-15(Sunday)(Healy's birthday) both of which are good for other reasons! Even so, it would be nice to be able to listen to this one here again!

Ray Augustine

San Diego
